patthana9.7:1.1_0: Nahetuñceva naahetukañca nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu ceva naahetuko ca nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana9.7:1.1_1: Nahetuñceva naahetukañca nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naahetuko ceva nana ca hetu nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana9.7:1.1_2: Nahetuñceva naahetukañca nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu ceva naahetuko ca nakusalo ca naahetuko ceva
patthana9.7:1.1_3: nana ca hetu nakusalo ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana9.7:2.1_0: Naahetukañceva nana ca hetuṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naahetuko ceva nana ca hetu nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana9.7:3.1_0: Nahetuñceva naahetukañca nakusalañca naahetukañceva nana ca hetuṁ nakusalañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu
patthana9.7:3.1_1: ceva naahetuko ca nakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana9.7:5.1_0: Nahetuñceva naahetukañca naakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu ceva naahetuko ca naakusalo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana9.7:7.1_0: Nahetuñceva naahetukañca naabyākataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nahetu ceva naahetuko ca naabyākato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
